---
title: Honey Cajun Chicken & Veggie Fries with Charred Pineapple Slaw & Garlic Aioli
description: Chicken and veggies for dinner is fun, but let’s really boost its appeal at the table by adding our Creole spice blend
to coat the chicken, then add in some charred pineapple, crunchy slaw and some colourful veggie fries. Put it all
together and you’ve got a very exciting dish to eat tonight!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
